*event_11
;[exp] onObjectTrigger

@notice text="If you want to fight dragons, press the button on the right."

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_12
;[exp] onObjectTrigger

@delevent
@se f=kacha
@wait time=800
@se f=fence
@wait time=100
@se f=fence
@wait time=100
@se f=fence
@switchfence x=21 y=8 way=s mode=open
@switchfence x=27 y=8 way=s mode=open
@switchfence x=33 y=8 way=s mode=open
@switchfence x=39 y=8 way=s mode=open
@switchfence x=45 y=8 way=s mode=open
@notice text="I heard the sound of several doors opening somewhere!"

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_13
;[exp] onObjectTrigger

@notice text="Light all the crystals to open the door to the abyss."

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_14
;[exp] true

@eval exp='game.map.bgm = "dragon"'
@eval exp='tf.chainedDragons = ["アクアドラゴン", "ブラックドラゴン", "ガスドラゴン", "フロストドラゴン", "ファイアドラゴン"]'
@wait time=500 cond='WAY != "s"'
@walk turn=s cond='WAY != "s"'
@wait time=500 cond='game.party.curY == 7'
@walk move=s cond='game.party.curY == 7'
@wait time=1000
@se f=roar
@fgf c=&'m[tf.chainedDragons[(game.party.curX - 21) \ 6]].img' left=450 top=-90
@wait time=1000
[texton]
A dragon appeared with a fierce roar![k]
[textoff]
@clf
@monster pos=3 name=&'tf.chainedDragons[(game.party.curX - 21) \ 6]'
@eval exp='tf.chainedDragons.erase((game.party.curX - 21) \ 6)'
@callbattle bgm=dragon gameover=true escape=false
@wait time=500
@se f=rockdrop
@wait time=1000
@se f=rockdrop
@wait time=1000
[texton]
Just when we thought the enemy defeated, something approaches from behind, making terrifying footsteps![k]
[textoff]
@wait time=500
@walk turn=n
@wait time=500
@se f=roar
@fgf c=&'m[tf.chainedDragons[2]].img' left=450 top=-90
@wait time=1000
[texton]
Suddenly, another dragon appeared from behind![k]
[textoff]
@clf
@monster pos=3 name=&'tf.chainedDragons[2]'
@eval exp='tf.chainedDragons.erase(2)'
@callbattle bgm=dragon gameover=true escape=false
@wait time=500
@se f=rockdrop
@wait time=1000
@se f=rockdrop
@wait time=1000
@se f=roar
@fgf c=&'m[tf.chainedDragons[1]].img' left=450 top=-90
@wait time=1000
[texton]
Another dragon has arrived![k]
It seems that the dragons in the other cages heard the noise and are approaching. Now that this has happened, we have no choice but to fight.[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@monster pos=3 name=&'tf.chainedDragons[1]'
@eval exp='tf.chainedDragons.erase(1)'
@callbattle bgm=dragon gameover=true escape=false
@wait time=500
@se f=rockdrop
@wait time=1000
@se f=roar
@fgf c=&'m[tf.chainedDragons[0]].img' left=450 top=-90
@wait time=1000
[texton]
Without a moment to catch our breath, another dragon arrived![k]
With the exit blocked, the only way to survive is to fight and win. We have no choice but to do it.[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@monster pos=3 name=&'tf.chainedDragons[0]'
@eval exp='tf.chainedDragons.erase(0)'
@callbattle bgm=dragon gameover=true escape=false
@wait time=500
@se f=roar
@fgf c=&'m[tf.chainedDragons[0]].img' left=450 top=-90
@wait time=1000
[texton]
Another dragon. The enemy was still there.[k]
The end of the battle is still nowhere in sight. Will we survive?[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@monster pos=3 name=&'tf.chainedDragons[0]'
@eval exp='tf.chainedDragons.erase(0)'
@eval exp='game.map.bgm = "cave"'
@callbattle bgm=dragon gameover=true escape=false
@wait time=1000
[texton]
...[k]
...It seems that the battle is finally over. We successfully defeated all of the dragons.[k]
[textoff]
@delevent

[eventoff]
